<p>35.5%です</p>
<p>とりあえず選挙に行きましょう<a class="link" href="https://x.com/osamusi0516/status/2065678980351664130?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"  target="_blank" rel="noopener"
    >June 13, 2026</a></p>
